testcase.name: OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Base API Route GET request to base API route must return 200 response
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Blob Upload Streamed PATCH request with blob in body should yield 202 response
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Blob Upload Streamed PUT request to session URL with digest should yield 201 response
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Blob Upload Monolithic GET nonexistent blob should result in 404 response
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Blob Upload Monolithic POST request with digest and blob should yield a 201
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Blob Upload Monolithic GET request to blob URL from prior request should yield 200
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Blob Upload Monolithic POST request should yield a session ID
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Blob Upload Monolithic PUT upload of a blob should yield a 201 Response
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Blob Upload Monolithic GET request to existing blob should yield 200 response
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Blob Upload Chunked Out-of-order blob upload should return 416
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Blob Upload Chunked PATCH request with first chunk should return 202
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Blob Upload Chunked PUT request with final chunk should return 201
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Manifest Upload GET nonexistent manifest should return 404
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Manifest Upload PUT should accept a manifest upload
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Manifest Upload GET request to manifest URL (digest) should yield 200 response
OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Tags List GET request to list tags should yield 200 response

OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Tags List GET start of tag is set by `last` query parameter

OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Error codes Response from DELETE request to manifest URL (tag) should have OCI-conforming code

OCI Distribution Conformance Tests Blob Delete GET request to deleted blob URL should yield 404 response
